{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make Bereavement allowance available to bereaved parents.",
        "additional_details": "It is wrong that this pressure is spur on lost grieving parents. No one is helping us. Everyone expects counselling to be thrown at you. \r\nYour just left struggling with everything it\u2019s all so very wrong.!\r\nI\u2019m not the only person this has happened too, I know a lot the system needs changing now",
        "background": "Once a child dies any state benefit your receive for them stops after 8 weeks. So in my case I need to find a job just 8 short weeks later or not be able to feed us or pay bills. Bereavement allowance is only paid to partners for 12 months! What is worse than losing a child. Parents count too",
